item.title: CVE-2021-2303|2024-09-26T14:10:41.638Z -- oracle%20corporation -- oss%20support%20tools
item.description: Vulnerability in the OSS Support Tools product of Oracle Support Tools (component: Diagnostic Assistant). The supported version that is affected is Prior to 2.12.41. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows high privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise OSS Support Tools. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized access to critical data or complete access to all OSS Support Tools accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 4.9 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:H/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N).
